90  ANY,

93 void append(ContainerBase& c, const std::initializer_list<StageType>& types, int runs = 0) {
94  for (StageType t : types) {
95  switch (t) {
96  case GEN:
97  c.add(std::make_unique<GeneratorMockup>(runs));
98  break;
99  case FW:
100  c.add(std::make_unique<ForwardMockup>(runs));
101  break;
102  case BW:
103  c.add(std::make_unique<BackwardMockup>(runs));
104  break;
105  case ANY:
106  c.add(std::make_unique<PropagatorMockup>(runs, runs));
107  break;
108  case CONN:
109  c.add(std::make_unique<ConnectMockup>(runs));
110  break;
111  }
112  }
113 }

196  void validateInit(bool start, bool end, bool expect_failure) { validateInit(start, end, {}, expect_failure); }
197 
198  void validateInit(bool start, bool end, const std::initializer_list<StageType>& types, bool expect_failure) {
199  reset(start, end);
200  append(container, types);
201  try {
202  container.init(robot_model);
203  // resolve interfaces based on provided external interface (start, end)
204  InterfaceFlags expected;
205  if (start)
206  expected |= WRITES_PREV_END;
207  else
208  expected |= READS_START;
209 
210  if (end)
211  expected |= WRITES_NEXT_START;
212  else
213  expected |= READS_END;
214 
215  container.pimpl()->resolveInterface(expected);
216  container.pimpl()->validateConnectivity();
217  if (!expect_failure)
218  return; // as expected
219  ADD_FAILURE() << "init() didn't recognize a failure condition as expected\n" << container;
220  } catch (const InitStageException& e) {
221  if (expect_failure) {
222  std::cout << "Expected " << e << "\n" << container;
223  return; // as expected
224  }
225  ADD_FAILURE() << "Unexpected " << e << "\n" << container;
226  } catch (const std::exception& e) {
227  ADD_FAILURE() << "unexpected exception thrown:\n" << e.what();
228  } catch (...) {
229  ADD_FAILURE() << "unexpected unknown exception thrown";
230  }
231  }
232 };

237  void validateOrder(const SerialContainerPrivate* container, const std::initializer_list<StagePrivate*>& expected) {
238  size_t num = container->children().size();
239  ASSERT_TRUE(num == expected.size()) << "different list lengths";
240 
241  // validate position()
242  EXPECT_EQ(container->children().begin(), container->childByIndex(-num));
243  EXPECT_EQ(container->children().end(), container->childByIndex(num));
244 
245  // validate order
246  size_t pos = 0;
247  auto exp_it = expected.begin();
248  for (auto it = container->children().begin(), end = container->children().end(); it != end;
249  ++it, ++exp_it, ++pos) {
250  StagePrivate* child = (*it)->pimpl();
251  EXPECT_EQ(child, *exp_it) << "wrong order";
252  EXPECT_EQ(child->parent()->pimpl(), container) << "wrong parent";
253  EXPECT_EQ(it, container->childByIndex(pos)) << "bad forward position resolution";
254  EXPECT_EQ(it, container->childByIndex(pos - num)) << "bad backward position resolution";
255  }
256  }
257 };

664  builder.addGroupChain("base", "c", "group");

666 
667  Task t("first");

669

671  auto ref = new stages::FixedState("fixed");
672  auto scene = std::make_shared<planning_scene::PlanningScene>(t.getRobotModel());
673  ref->setState(scene);
674

692  } catch (const InitStageException& e) {
